      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches or dents, and the interior is pristine and free of any wear or odors. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. This is a rare opportunity to own a pre-owned vehicle that is essentially in brand-new condition.",
