      "description": "Looking for a rewarding weekend project? This vehicle is the perfect canvas for a DIY enthusiast! While it is in poor condition and needs a fair amount of work to get back into top shape, it offers a fantastic opportunity to own a car at a budget-friendly price. It's ready for someone with the right tools and passion to give it a second life!",
